on\"><a href=\"https://www.canada.ca/en/services/environment.html\" role=\"menuitem\" tabindex=\"-1\">Environment and natural resources</a></li>\n<li role=\"presentation\"><a href=\"https://www.canada.ca/en/services/defence.html\" role=\"menuitem\" tabindex=\"-1\">National security and defence</a></li>\n<li role=\"presentation\"><a href=\"https://www.canada.ca/en/services/culture.html\" role=\"menuitem\" tabindex=\"-1\">Culture, history and sport</a></li>\n<li role=\"presentation\"><a href=\"https://www.canada.ca/en/services/policing.html\" role=\"menuitem\" tabindex=\"-1\">Policing, justice and emergencies</a></li>\n<li role=\"presentation\"><a href=\"https://www.canada.ca/en/services/transport.html\" role=\"menuitem\" tabindex=\"-1\">Transport and infrastructure</a></li>\n<li role=\"presentation\"><a href=\"https://www.international.gc.ca/world-monde/index.aspx?lang=eng\" role=\"menuitem\" tabindex=\"-1\">Canada and the world</a></li>\n<li role=\"presentation\"><a href=\"https://www.canada.ca/en/services/finance.html\" role=\"menuitem\" tabindex=\"-1\">Money and finances</a></li>\n<li role=\"presentation\"><a href=\"https://www.canada.ca/en/services/science.html\" role=\"menuitem\" tabindex=\"-1\">Science and innovation</a></li>\n<li role=\"presentation\"><a href=\"https://www.canada.ca/en/services/life-events.html\" role=\"menuitem\" tabindex=\"-1\">Manage life events</a></li>\n</ul>\n</nav>\n</div>\n</div></div>\n<nav id=\"wb-bc\" property=\"breadcrumb\"><h2 class=\"wb-inv\">You are here:</h2><div class=\"container\"><ol class=\"breadcrumb\">\n<li><a href=\"/en.html\">Canada.ca</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/en/services/immigration-citizenship.html\">Immigration and citizenship</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/en/immigration-refugees-citizenship/services/canadian-citizenship.html\">Canadian citizenship</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/en/immigration-refugees-citizenship/services/canadian-citizenship/stateless.html\">Canadian citizenship for stateless people</a></li>\n</ol></div></nav>\n</header>\n</div>\n</div>\n<main class=\"container\" property=\"mainContentOfPage\" resource=\"#wb-main\" typeof=\"WebPageElement\">\n<div class=\"mwsgeneric-base-html parbase section\">\n<!-- 1: GC Subway navigation -->\n<nav class=\"gc-subway provisional\">\n<h1>Apply for Canadian citizenship: Stateless people</h1>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/en/immigration-refugees-citizenship/services/canadian-citizenship/stateless/who.html\">Who can apply</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/en/immigration-refugees-citizenship/services/canadian-citizenship/stateless/forms-documents.html\">Get the forms and documents</a>\n</li>\n<li><a class=\"active\" href=\"/en/immigration-refugees-citizenship/services/canadian-citizenship/stateless/submit.html\">Submit your application</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/en/immigration-refugees-citizenship/services/canadian-citizenship/stateless/wait.html\">Wait for a decision</a></li>\n</ul>\n</nav>\n<!-- 2: Title -->\n<h1 class=\"gc-thickline\" id=\"wb-cont\" property=\"name\">Submit your application</h1>\n<div data-wb-jsonmanager='{\n            \"url\": \"/content/dam/ircc/documents/json/fees.json\",\n            \"name\": \"fee\"\n            }' id=\"jsonmanagerfees\"> </div>\n<p>When your forms and documents are ready, you can</p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#pay\">pay the application fees</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#mail\">mail your application</a></li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"well\">\n<p>If you haven’t done so already, find out how to <a href=\"/en/immigration-refugees-citizenship/services/canadian-citizenship/stateless/forms-documents.html\">prepare  the forms and documents</a>.</p>\n</div>\n<ol class=\"lst-stps ld-zr\">\n<li><h2 class=\"mrgn-tp-0\" id=\"pay\">Pay the application fees</h2>\n<p>The citizenship application fee for a stateless person is <span data-json-replace=\"#[fee]/cit-right/en\"><strong>[Error loading fee. <a href=\"https://ircc.canada.ca/english/information/fees/fees.asp\">Check the fee list</a>.]</strong></span>.</p>\n<h3>How to pay</h3>\n<p>Pay the fee only when you’re ready to submit your application.</p>\n<ol>\n<li>Sign in to our online payment system.\n                <ul>\n<li>Create an account if you don’t have one.</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>Pay your fees.</li>\n<li>Print and include the receipt with your application.</li>\n</ol>\n<p class=\"mrgn-tp-md\">If you’re submitting more than 1 application at the same time, you can pay all the fees together (1 receipt) or separately (many receipts). Include a copy of your receipt in each application.</p>\n<p><a class=\"btn btn-primary\" href=\"https://ircc.canada.ca/english/information/fees/pay.asp\">Pay your fees online</a></p>\n<details>\n<summary><h3 class=\"fnt-nrml lead\">If you don’t pay the correct amount</h3></summary>\n<p><strong>If you don’t pay enough</strong>, we’ll return the entire application. We’ll start processing the application only after we receive the full amount of the fee.</p>\n<p><strong>If you pay too much</strong>, we’ll refund the difference and process your application normally.</p>\n</details>\n<details>\n<summary><h3 class=\"fnt-nrml lead\">Getting a refund</h3></summary>\n<p>You can get a full refund for your application fee if you cancel or abandon your application. We’ll send it to the person named in the “Payer Information” section of the receipt.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://ircc.canada.ca/english/information/fees/refund.asp\">Learn how to request a refund if you cancel or abandon your application.</a></p>\n</details>\n</li>\n<li><h2 class=\"mrgn-tp-0\" id=\"mail\">Mail your application</h2>\n<!-- reference begins-->\n<div data-ajax-append=\"/content/canadasite/en/immigration-refugees-citizenship/services/reference-include/canadapost-citimmtr-eng.html#canadapost-citimmtr-eng-id1\"></div>\n<!-- reference ends-->\n<p>To avoid delays or a return of your application package, follow these steps before you mail it.</p>\n<ol class=\"lst-stps-sub\">\n<li>Before you sign the form\n            <ul>\n<li>Confirm you still meet the citizenship eligibility requirements.</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>Check completeness\n            <ul>\n<li>Confirm that you have included every required form, document and payment receipt.</li>\n<li>If applying as a family or a group, put all complete applications and receipts in one envelope so that we can process them together.</li>\n<li>If any application is incomplete, we will return the entire package </li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>Sign and date the form\n            <ul>\n<li>Sign the application form yourself.</li>\n<li>Use the actual date you sign the form. Do not back-date or post-date.</li>\n<li>The date you sign your application form must be the date you enter in the physical presence calculation section (section 9, line B).</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>Send the package right away\n \n            <ul>\n<li>Courier or mail the application package within 90 days of the signature date.\n                    <ul>\n<li><strong>Tracking your application:</strong> We recommend that you use a postal or courier service with tracking so that you have proof your application was delivered. <a href=\"https://ircc.canada.ca/english/helpcentre/answer.asp?amp;top=&amp;qnum=028\">Find out how to check if your application has been received</a>.</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>We’ll return the package if it arrives after 90 days.</li>\n</ul>\n<p class=\"mrgn-tp-md\">Send your application package to the appropriate address:</p>\n<div class=\"cnjnctn-type-or cnjnctn-sm\">\n<section class=\"cnjnctn-col\">\n<h3 class=\"h5 mrgn-tp-0\">Courier<span class=\"wb-inv\">: Option 1 of 2</span></h3>\n<p class=\"text-uppercase\">IRCC Digitization Centre – Citizenship<br/>\n                3050 Wilson Ave<br/>\n                New Waterford NS  B1H 5V8</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"cnjnctn-col\">\n<h3 class=\"h5 mrgn-tp-0\">Regular mail<span class=\"wb-inv\">: Option 2 of 2</span></h3>\n<p class=\"text-uppercase\">Case Processing Centre – Sydney<br/>\n                Citizenship Grants<br/>\n                Po Box 7000<br/>\n                Sydney NS  B1P 6V6</p>\n</section>\n</div>\n</li>\n</ol>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<nav class=\"gc-subway-pagination\">\n<h2 class=\"wb-inv\">Document navigation</h2>\n<ul class=\"pager\">\n<li class=\"next\"><a href=\"/en/immigration-refugees-citizenship/services/canadian-citizenship/stateless/wait.html\" rel=\"next\"><span class=\"wb-inv\">Next: </span>Wait for a decision</a></li>\n</ul>\n</nav>\n</div>\n<section class=\"pagedetails\">\n<h2 class=\"wb-inv\">Page details</h2>\n<div class=\"row\">\n<div class=\"col-sm-8 col-md-9 col-lg-9\">\n<div class=\"wb-disable-allow\" data-ajax-replace=\"/etc/designs/canada/wet-boew/assets/feedback/page-feedback-en.html\">\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<gcds-date-modified>\n\t2025-09-29\n</gcds-date-modified>\n</section>\n</main>\n<div class=\"newpar new section\">\n</div>\n<div class=\"par iparys_inherited\">\n</div>\n<div class=\"newpar new section\">\n</div>\n<div class=\"par iparys_inherited\">\n<div class=\"global-footer\">\n<footer id=\"wb-info\">\n<h2 class=\"wb-inv\">About this site</h2>\n<div class=\"gc-contextual\"><div class=\"container\">\n<nav>\n<h3>Immigration and citizenship</h3>\n<ul class=\"list-col-xs-1 list-col-sm-2 list-col-md-3\">\n<li><a href=\"https://ircc.canada.ca/english/helpcentre/results-by-topic.asp?top=5\">Help Centre</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/en/immigration-refugees-citizenship/corporate/contact-ircc.html\">Contact us</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/en/immigration-refugees-citizenship/services/application/check-status.html\">Check your application status</a></li>\n</ul>\n</nav>\n</div></div>\n<div class=\"gc-main-footer\">\n<div class=\"container\">\n<nav>\n<h3>Government of Canada</h3>\n<ul class=\"list-col-xs-1 list-col-sm-2 list-col-md-3\">\n<li><a href=\"/en/contact.html\">All contacts</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/en/government/dept.html\">Departments and agencies</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/en/government/system.html\">About government</a></li>\n</ul>\n<h4><span class=\"wb-inv\">Themes and topics</span>